\ A continuation captured before `forget` must not be resumable. forget
\ rewinds the dictionary; a later redefinition then overwrites the cells
\ resume_ip points into, and vocab.here climbs back past resume_ip -- so a
\ range check on resume_ip cannot detect the staleness. A forget-generation
\ stamp on the continuation, compared at resume, rejects it cleanly instead
\ of jumping into overwritten code (which SIGSEGVs without the guard).
variable K
: shifter shift ;
: ex1 reset 99 shifter 2 * ;
ex1 swap drop to K
forget shifter
: a 1 + ; : b a a a ; : c b b b ; : d c c c ;
5 K resume . cr
